   "widgets_values": [
    "THE MOVE\n\n1. 📽 Project ON (default). Orbit to check coverage.\n2. 🧭 Safe Zone probe-renders around the recovered camera and CLAMPS\n   the orbit to the measured hole-free arc — your move stays inside\n   what actually exists.\n3. 🎥 Camera Path → a preset (Dolly In / Orbit L) or fly-nav\n   keyframes → ▶ Play → ⏺ Bake Path.\n4. Bake fills path_frames (→ a Video Combine node, NOT installed\n   here) and camera_path (→ the .usda export, MUTED until baked —\n   un-mute it after ⏺ Bake or it errors by design).\n\nThe .nk carries every layer with its OWN camera; the move can also\nbe authored in Nuke against the same geometry."
